==基礎設施==
2015年3月27日，杰克逊市市长托尼·亚伯 (Tony Yarber) 发布了交通（地面坑窪）和水利基础设施（水管中断）的紧急状态。在2014-2015年的严冬天气之后，杰克逊的水利基础设施系统狀況日益惡化。<ref name="wapt">{{Cite news|url = http://www.wapt.com/news/central-mississippi/jackson/jackson-mayor-seeks-emergency-loan-to-pay-for-water-repairs/32364888|title = Jackson mayor seeks emergency loan to pay for water repairs|last = Simmons|first = Scott|date = April 14, 2015|work = 16 WAPT News|access-date = April 17, 2015|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150417060149/http://www.wapt.com/news/central-mississippi/jackson/jackson-mayor-seeks-emergency-loan-to-pay-for-water-repairs/32364888|archive-date = April 17, 2015|url-status = live}}</ref><ref name="tidaily">{{Cite news|url = http://tinewsdaily.com/stories/510504641-jackson-miss-mayor-declares-infrastructure-emergency|title = Jackson, Miss., mayor declares infrastructure emergency|date = March 27, 2015|work = TI News Daily|access-date = April 17, 2015|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150417061204/http://tinewsdaily.com/stories/510504641-jackson-miss-mayor-declares-infrastructure-emergency|archive-date = April 17, 2015|url-status = live}}</ref>

